title: Darwin's Doubt and Intelligent Design - Collection 9
description:
Darwin's Doubt and Intelligent Design - Collection 9:

We have 18 titles here:

-  Bird - Chaos and Life; Complexity and Order in Evolution and Thought (2003)

-  Drummond - The Ascent of Man (1894, 2009)

-  Gonzalez & Richards - The Privileged Planet; How Our Place in the Cosmos is Designed for Discovery (2004)

-  Harold - In Search of Cell History; the Evolution of Life's Building Blocks (2014)

-  Hopwood - Haeckel's Embryos; Images, Evolution, and Fraud (2015)

-  Kolter & Maloy (Eds.) - Microbes and Evolution; the World That Darwin Never Saw (2012)

-  Lane - The Vital Question; Why Is Life the Way It Is (2015)

-  Patel - Music, Language, and the Brain (2008)

-  Pereltsvaig & Lewis - The Indo-European Controversy; Facts and Fallacies in Historical Linguistics (2015)

-  Reid - Biological Emergences; Evolution by Natural Experiment (2007)

-  Roth - The Long Evolution of Brains and Minds (2013)

-  Roughgarden - The Genial Gene; Deconstructing Darwinian Selfishness (2009)

-  Scott - The Nonlinear Universe; Chaos, Emergence, Life (2007)

-  Stoczkowski - Explaining Human Origins Myth, Imagination, and Conjecture (2002)

-  Tattersall - Masters of the Planet; the Search for Our Human Origins (2012)

-  Wallace - Beasts of Eden; Walking Whales, Dawn Horses, and Other Enigmas of Mammal Evolution (2004)

-  Wiker - 10 Books That Screwed Up the World, and 5 Others That Didn't Help (2008)

-  Yahya - Atlas of Creation, Vol. 4 (2012)
